sources.title: JacksTheBoy
sources.description: “Diverting entertainment” “Creaky fun” (IMDB reviews quotes). Jack Hulbert and Cicely Courtneidge costarr in this fast-talking comedy of the London Metropolitan Police with a bit of music, dance and romance in the mix. IMDB rating 5.9. Directed by Walter Forde. UK release 1932. US release 1933. Complete print (1940 UK re-release). A.K.A. "Night and Day" CAST NOTE: The screen debuts of Jack Hulbert and Cicely Courtneidge who were husband and wife in real life.
